{"tid":1618840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"衛生處佩戴口罩指引","createTime":"2019-10-04T06:40:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T06:40:12.000Z","uid":269083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"48214a73a94626198c19234dbf0c11b4478d3c51","tid":1618840,"uid":269083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:40:12.000Z","msg":"為他人着想，當我們出現呼吸道感染病徵時 (咳嗽或打噴嚏...) 就記得要帶口罩。<br />\n<br />\n衛生處佩戴口罩指引：<br />\n<br />\n何時要佩戴口罩？<br />\n1. 保護自己：當我們需<br />\n要照顧呼吸道受感染<br />\n的患者時；或在流<br />\n感大流行／高峰期期<br />\n間進入醫院或診所。<br />\n<br />\n2. 保護他人避免受感染：<br />\n當我們出現呼吸道感染病徵時，如發燒、流<br />\n鼻水、咳嗽或打噴嚏等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chp.gov.hk/files/her/use_mask_properly_pamphlet.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chp.gov.hk%2Ffiles%2Fher%2Fuse_mask_properly_pamphlet.pdf&d=A2ufI7QLpLp1ny1o1CjT3vaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=fe1dca8e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chp.gov.hk/files/her/use_mask_properly_pamphlet.pdf</a>"}]}